# Per-paper output directories (extracted figures/tables are copyrighted by the
# paper's publisher). Slug convention per paper-to-deck SKILL.md Step 1:
#   <first-author-surname>-<year>-<topic>  e.g. dobrescu-2026-picc
#   <trial-acronym>[-trial|-study]         e.g. orchestra-trial
# Add each new paper's output directory explicitly here so we don't accidentally
# commit extracted artefacts. A broad glob would risk ignoring skill internals.
dobrescu-2026-picc/
tande-2026-spinal-epidural-abscess/

# OpenEvidence MCP integration · personal session data
# These MUST never ship publicly, even if _private/ is ever relaxed:
#   - cookies.json        · your OE auth session
#   - playwright-profile/ · your Playwright-managed browser profile
cookies.json
playwright-profile/
openevidence-mcp/

